attributes.field: CBZ Loan Scheme Account Terms & Conditions
attributes.value: I hereby request the CBZ Bank Limited (CBZ or 'the bank') to open a CBZ Loan Scheme Account ('the loan') in my name and I hereby agree to abide by the following terms and conditions as well as any other conditions as may come into being from time to time.

clauses: Interest shall be accrued daily, charged and capitalized monthly at Libor plus a margin to be advised by the Bank in the offer letter and as reviewed from time to time.
CBZ is hereby authorized to apportion the monthly repayments between interest and capital loan reductions as the bank may desire and to debit my Account with all such monthly repayments.
To be recovered upon establishment and/or on re-advancement of the loan at 3.5% or a minimum of USD 17.50.
The above fees will be paid in cash as a deduction from the loan proceeds.

A non-refundable loan processing fee of USD7.50 shall be recoverable upfront from applicant’s account upon submission of loan form and the loan processing fee is not a guarantee that the application will be successful.
My salary is to be paid directly from my employer into Account on a monthly basis.

Failure by me to meet the requirements of 3.1 above shall render the outstanding loan balance plus accrued interest immediately due and payable, notwithstanding the fact that my monthly repayments may be up to date at the time the breach is committed.
